---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import GameEmbed from "../../components/GameEmbed.astro";

const EMBED_ID = "4269156";
const EMBED_WIDTH = 1280;
const EMBED_HEIGHT = 740;

const COVER = "/TCOLSS.png";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Circle of Life — Will Moppel"
  description="2D puzzle platformer built in Unreal Engine. Solve puzzles by working with past versions of yourself."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-base">

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-8 pb-2">
      <a
        href="/#projects"
        class="font-body text-sm text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors"
      >
        ← Back to projects
      </a>
    </div>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">

      <div class="pt-10 pb-12">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">
          The Circle of Life
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-muted">
          Solve puzzles by working with past versions of yourself.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mb-16">
        <GameEmbed
          title="The Circle of Life"
          embedId={EMBED_ID}
          itchUrl="https://cactusspike.itch.io/the-circle-of-life"
          cover={COVER}
          embedWidth={EMBED_WIDTH}
          embedHeight={EMBED_HEIGHT}
          accentColor="4d8bff"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Details block -->
      <div class="mb-16 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 border-t border-line pt-10">
        <div>
          <p class="font-body text-xs text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Role</p>
          <p class="font-body text-ink">
            Developer
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-body text-xs text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Engine</p>
          <p class="font-body text-ink">
            Unreal Engine
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-body text-xs text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Tools &amp; Tech</p>
          <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 list-none p-0 m-0 mt-1">
            <li class="font-body text-xs text-muted bg-surface-2 border border-line rounded px-3 py-1">Blueprints</li>
            <li class="font-body text-xs text-muted bg-surface-2 border border-line rounded px-3 py-1">C++</li>
            <li class="font-body text-xs text-muted bg-surface-2 border border-line rounded px-3 py-1">Input Capture</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Description -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-5 font-body text-muted leading-relaxed mb-16">
        <p>Select your character with 1, 2, or 3, and then control them with the arrow keys. Then pick a different character,
          and the first character repeats your exact moves, which lets you solve puzzles by working with your past self. Your goal is 
          to get all of the characters to burn in the fire and that's how you win and move to the next level.</p>
          <p>I built this game for a game jam with the theme "rebirth." I wanted to make a 2D platformer, 
          but I found that a lot of them do the same things, and I wanted to make something different, so I came up with this idea.
          After coming up with and programming the core mechanic it was really fun for me to design chalenging levels.</p>
          <p>After finishing the project, I realized that since the characters record inputs instead of locations,
          the frame rate can cause some bugs where the characters aren't where they should be. If I were to continue working on this project, I would
          fix that, probably by stabilizing the frame rate, to make the gameplay smoother in the future. The trick to get around it is to walk against
          a corner every so often to make sure your position is consistent, but as the player you shouldn't have to do that.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 border-t border-line pt-10">
        <a
          href="https://cactusspike.itch.io/the-circle-of-life"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="font-body text-sm font-semibold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg bg-accent text-ink hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Play on itch.io ↗
        </a>
      </div>

    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
